{"tid":1354772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 我宣佈729會係第一次成功嘅罷工運動","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T20:14:17.000Z","uid":159428,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7ff1ad03c95ffb8058d55b24f6c909af1d5627","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:07:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[光復香港 時代革命] 革命口號比你想像中重要 而且好有用 &ndash; 關於三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我相信有非常多香港人都係想罷工，只係唔敢，所以要製造一個客觀條件令依個運動成功。</span>香港人唔係唔想付出，只係要無後果嘅付出。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">靈感黎自前日見到有巴打分享：<br />\n烏克蘭朋友提議，將「光復香港 時代革命」變成義士之間打招呼用語<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336769</a></span><br />\n<br />\n721晚發夢，手足終於嗌啱口號，親身感受到士氣差幾皮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動</span> (又或者係將來嘅其他偏地開花運動) <span style=\"color: red;\">唔同連儂牆或者出黎遊行集會，後者出現得喺某個地方都大致假定係同路人。</span>返工時間要癱瘓地鐵，咁早好多時都係自己一個人，未必約得到朋友同行，又未必可以用黑衫介定自己人。淆底係好正常，<span style=\"color: red;\">好少人敢出黎帶頭</span>，怕得自己一個有起事上黎孤立無援。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以要搵同路人</span></span>，留意到有交流嘅人，用革命口號打招呼。<br />\nA（伸手）：光復香港<br />\nB（握手）：時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">基本上搵到3~5個人以上組隊已經可以互相照應。</span><br />\n打機打副本都要搵陌生人組隊先，行動黎講小隊組織一定係最有效率。依一層唔單止係講緊不合作運動 。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港打工嘅一眾負責任嘅奴隸，同上頭解釋話罷工同被罷工係差好遠。客觀條件成立的話，即使你係活動參與者，港鐵賴屎你先可以<span style=\"color: red;\">「賴自己係被罷工」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b652893c6922d3a037308a7f79b2d57e23d2a616","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onWQh8Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonWQh8Q.gif&h=2db6bcd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第二 係革命手勢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用口號打招呼有個問題，無啦啦見人就走埋去講光復香港，有一定機會點錯相，會開口既人亦一定唔佔多數。<br />\nA（伸手）：光復香港<br />\nB（我無嘢講）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以需要一個被動嘅signal。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要好出面，只要單手做出革命手勢。</span>會留意到既同路人就會留意到，就會埋堆打招呼。其實當年黃絲帶係幾好，不過已經被膠化。做乜野signal依一點我覺得仲有討論空間，不過signal都唔一定得一個，只要大家都知咩事就得。<br />\n<br />\n另外，依個亦不失為一個好機會俾我地喺公眾場合訓練assemble，未來話唔定連登甚至TG會收皮。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n729大家可以試下， 愈普及愈有用。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3aa0fcbcca297bdc27413d42a53e60ec1796e88c","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第三 地點時間 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n地點問題比較容易解決，人多嘅大型轉車站月台，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">只係用黎組隊</span>。即係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">金鐘</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\">、九龍塘、太子、旺角、油塘、大圍</span>依啲大站。唔需要刻意定死一個地方，邊度人多邊度就機會大，BE WATER，況且搵到兩三個隊友就可以開始行事。<br />\n<br />\n時間依個問題就比較難搞，香港人都係鐘意遲到。因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愈早有人開始行動係愈有利</span></span>，受影響嘅人同時間先夠多，而且會鼓勵到更多人參與。<span style=\"color: red;\">建議0715前就要到大站，0730前一定要有人開始行動</span> (講早啲反正你地都會遲)。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"690f6d13fb4c6181f4343b50d372ddb2174cfde4","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解要729？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其一，我<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對相信727、728會係一場苦戰，因為敵人除左有傀儡政權下嘅黑警以外仲有中央指使嘅鄉黑</span>。729星期一罷工可以<span style=\"color: red;\">為727、728作掩護</span>，俾多一日時間前線行動又好休息又好。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，罷工都需要時間預備、做文宣。<span style=\"color: red;\">612返工日子都有咁多人出現除左因為形勢危急之外，而且事前仲有大大小小企業響應、民陣呼籲，為運動打頭炮。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef09968c505ca9c5c1ee5d316c77ffee88c571a6","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <ins>Reference:</ins><br />\n[行動升級] 729 全港大罷工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/doDGfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/doDGfS</a><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 有痴線佬係地鐵裸跑導致延誤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dopRgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dopRgS</a><br />\n<br />\n[三罷] 地球人已阻止唔到香港人返工 － 癱瘓交通 罷工罷市罷課<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dotfjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dotfjS</a><br />\n<br />\n講左好多次 長期全港罷工前設係癱瘓交通<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351504</a><br />\n<ins><br />\n轉貼三罷交癱Tg link:</ins><br />\n荃灣紅綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxMVahIL7PYl4fOjGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhPxMVahIL7PYl4fOjGg&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=8b5f7c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxMVahIL7PYl4fOjGg</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘綠綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxRiXvtrWWVQ7PnDzg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhPxRiXvtrWWVQ7PnDzg&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=cd3a8fb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxRiXvtrWWVQ7PnDzg</a><br />\n<br />\n港島藍綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxLvNZEbZNdXzF396Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhPxLvNZEbZNdXzF396Q&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=d565f2dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxLvNZEbZNdXzF396Q</a><br />\n<br />\n東鐵綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxNQb4b64pjyMRLQ5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhPxNQb4b64pjyMRLQ5w&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=bb15fd9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxNQb4b64pjyMRLQ5w</a><br />\n<br />\n西鐵綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxaZqPi1l-PyBz_e6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhPxaZqPi1l-PyBz_e6g&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=5e54181a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhPxaZqPi1l-PyBz_e6g</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fee8f00bb482d52d04cfb51cd1d2f75a0d2d5baa","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔去搞政治<br />\n政治就會搞你</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n全 民 皆 兵 ！</span></span>"},{"pid":"18428a48dd40074845270a568b7549ebe1eaea24","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">罷工前設係交通癱瘓！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc51f290856082101bf5880d27988c69e7d3f3e0","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">729 全港大罷工！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c531d432c9df5afa21eeff7afc3b0ab62ec25577","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d18a6378ec2d9a52ab4427d4d6b17224faa9a31a","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da5d9b8817cd5ace1b4990633119f13be4e1808e","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99bd167639012df4fc3f50de0c55b01792003990","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58567faa2141da5ccde30bdbec14e6ead3319d94","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dfef2e256edd7fddd23240809c7072f5de0e5a","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5e4fdee151b4079f622b3013e5934fdefa3239","tid":1354772,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb13f421347dfb0846fd1116edd03e0b31eb9d4e","tid":1354772,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"屌你出面講緊724<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ef0eddf91b7bbb4fee194932ce680d80eeec87","tid":1354772,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:50:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"3f87244fb1698f3d2d263b66461395fd01d7d0d3","tid":1354772,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:56:19.000Z","msg":"夾下日子先好喎"},{"pid":"22e3dde7c0747f6d6a38a53047e717ba0a22253a","tid":1354772,"uid":181221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"103a91b4523585b33418fe6df29dc6e1adb6c42c","tid":1354772,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持全民戴頭盔搭地鐵返工</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你罷工罷課 你地唔夠膽<br />\n咁帶個頭盔返工得喇掛 咁都做唔到<br />\n唔戴住係頭 都扣係個袋喇</span><br />\n<br />\n[多字] 體感話我知 前線同後排支援斷纜斷得十分之嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344268</a>"},{"pid":"36b0d3a2e3777dd765663a80c42ea4e4989d3149","tid":1354772,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:59:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0913b75b064423d217b4af6da991c8ea3c14202","tid":1354772,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:02:23.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"93af7d7356b300d759574a52b738f52fb4eca16f","tid":1354772,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T20:14:17.000Z","msg":"一定要由起點站做 等開唔到車<br />\n否則中間可能有人已經落車翻工"}]}